         <p>The total number of fruit in this set is 9.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
         <p><abbr title=""><sup>4</sup>⁄<sub>3</sub></abbr> describes the part-part relationship of this container of filled to not filled.</p>
         <div class="center"><img src="/images/attention/fracAtt13.png" alt="fruits" /></div>
         <p>The total number of equi-partitions in the whole container is 7.</p>
      </div>
   </div>
