                  <div class="col-md-6"><b>Unit Fractions</b>
   <p>Digits in both the numerator and the denominator are integers; the numerator = 1.</p>
   <p><abbr title=""><sup>1</sup>⁄<sub>2</sub></abbr> <abbr title=""><sup>1</sup>⁄<sub>15</sub></abbr> <abbr title=""><sup>1</sup>⁄<sub>29</sub></abbr></p></div>
               </div>
            </td>
            <td>
               <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-md-6"><b>Mixed Fractions</b>
   <p>A quantity represented by an integer and a proper fraction</p>
   <p>3<abbr title=""><sup>4</sup>⁄<sub>5</sub></abbr> 12<abbr title=""><sup>1</sup>⁄<sub>29</sub></abbr> 7<abbr title=""><sup>21</sup>⁄<sub>26</sub></abbr></p></div>
                  <div class="col-md-6"><b>Improper Fractions</b>
   <p>Digits in both the numerator and the denominator are integers; the numerator > the denominator.</p>
   <p><abbr title=""><sup>3</sup>⁄<sub>2</sub></abbr> <abbr title=""><sup>125</sup>⁄<sub>28</sub></abbr> </p></div>
